					.form-group
						div(class="col-sm-6")
							a(href="http://eepurl.com/YUL55") Powered by MailChimp
			
			p Want to get in touch with us? Drop us a line at 
				a(href="mailto:sales@auditionsoftware.com") sales@auditionsoftware.com